title: July Sublet in Andersonville w/ option to renew!
posting_body: ['unfurnished july sublet with option to renew in the heart of andersonville!', 'walking distance from N. Clark and Broadway, redline, clark bus, coffee, shops, restaurants etc. building has assured me that nobody has signed a lease yet for after July so this is a great option for someone who wants long term housing too.', 'water and heat included.', 'has outdoor space & bike room.', 'hardwood floors.', 'lots of west facing windows.', 'please text (512)694-7303 for info.']
